reviewText: To this day I remember to look BEFORE I leap! Whether attempting a high dive or suicide, my thoughts always return to the sage words of the robot host. Thanks Official Kids Safety Quiz!

YOu need to see this to believe it.  A robot comes out of the chalkboard and teaches a class about safety via a televised game show. I don't want to give away the ending but...who am I kidding... THEY ALL BECOME A+ Safety Experts!!!
